{"tid":154983,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得二胡係世界級咁正","createTime":"2017-03-13T16:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T17:37:14.000Z","uid":62852,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f17b3cdc0f346fffcef5b2e8395121bac10348a","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得二胡好好聽，有種憂鬱既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n今日發生左D唔開心既事，成晚都覺得個心屈住屈住咁，<br />\n咁啱youtube自動播放到周董既蘭亭序，二胡前奏一出即刻喊左出黎，二胡聲好似刺穿左個心咁，完全停唔到。<br />\n<br />\n之前有諗過學二胡，係大陸見到有就買左個二胡番屋企，但之後搵唔到邊度有得學，就算有都好似要係好遠學（住北區），所以冇左回事，依家好想學番。<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時完全唔喊，但睇電影成日喊<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"87195065005e6deb6d981d96f6634dcca47a1db2","tid":154983,"uid":18029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"之前學過一年，都係湯雞咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ca2e0dbc36f1461a640ee2a1b5ed646de49f48","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4121225ee9af855a0d24f093f23a3b65cd161198","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d98b08570f3f32cfc818312a6df5cb65028daaa","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b3d4a2c63d34ddc7c39699978457074dec6ffb","tid":154983,"uid":84478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"蘭亭序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c3b6c83e04d373beb258dec84308bae8ae995b","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前學過一年，都係湯雞咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching係邊學架？？<br />\n<br />\n我果時買番黎都拉到湯雞咁，仲斷左幾條毛，所以放棄左"},{"pid":"353b6fd9f87780b91b31714dd2394790bab45b97","tid":154983,"uid":34686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"好似話二胡係最似人聲嘅樂器,有時聽二胡係幾有感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c195b4793af859fa081cea392495826ce7b0b4","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話二胡係最似人聲嘅樂器,有時聽二胡係幾有感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又未聽過，但我聽過首唔知叫賽馬定係咩既二胡曲，拉得真係好鬼似馬聲"},{"pid":"98879c4fab8790f0a61ba2ce5f1a54e5204434d5","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf015eba8005348edd549c5e6c71aff38f9357f","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b81cdc7c5a5a99440d202e8a533ce3829787c6","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c4a97fa0d7f519894ebd29b768f03f42116ede","tid":154983,"uid":62852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"